Improvements=============Changes 3.8.1* MacOS 9 support improved (proportional scroll bards, proxy icon, path display)* AppleScript support improved* Electric Image export added* PDF writer will now get the correct image name* BUM import and export added* NAA/IPTC import added* PICT from resource import and export added* 3 color BIORAD files can no be imported as an animation* fill requires now less memory and is faster* option to display new folder in the same browser window added* 300x300 and 400x400 as option to browser added* batch function pict improved (supports now insertion of an image with opacy)* support for TWAIN 1.7 added (only PPC)* rename option in convert more improved* option to change frame delay for all frames added* option to set and get color space with AppleScript added* margins added to print dialog * support for color pdb import and export added* support for import of very large images added* internal memory handling changed* many bug fixes and internal changesChanges 3.8* basic applescript support added (only PPC version)* script menu added (only PPC version)* import of IMQ added* import and export of NOL and NGG added* import of NCG added* import of doodle (uncompressed/compressed) and koala format added* import of DPX added* TCL image import/export added* import and export of JIF added* export of BLD added* export of ascii pbm added* TWAIN import added* DICOM import improved* TIFF import improved * BIORAD import improved* edit support events added* Appearance support improved* typing bugs during html creation fixed* bug during decompression of YCC-TIFFs fixed* scaling bug in preview during effect dialogs fixed* bug during display of QuickTime movie references in the browser fixed* x11 import will now ignore comment lines* shift click works now correctly in the browser* lossless JPEG rotation displays now a dialog during long operations* bug in copy as HTML fixed* bug with - in formats via AppleScript fixed* update bug in the browser fixed* possible bug with wrong icons in the browser fixed* slideshow options for effects improved* bug in rename in convert more fixed* scale will now check the rescale window option* redraw problem in toolbar window in the slideshow fixed* position bug in layout window fixed* bug with menu shortcut fixed* File Info dialog is now appearance compatible* copy EXIF as TEXT added* option for rescale window size after scale added* delete resource will now ignore alias files* bug in drawing lines with arrows fixed* split will now add the number before the extension (for dos compatibility)* GraphicConverter will now ignore the bad y resolution settings of JPEGs from Painter* bug in WBMP export/import with more than 128 pixels fixed* dialog with option before printing of large images added* bug in plug-in support fixed* pcx detection improved* option for display unknown TIF tags added* option for zero based coordinates added* crash after slideshow with find on 68K Macs fixed* crash after opening info window on pre MacOS 8 systems fixed* dimension menu looks now better with pre MacOS 8 systems* support for live scrolling (only PPC with MacOS 8 or later) added* shift key works now correct for circular selections* support for circular selections added* option for disabling the text in the preview of the browser fixed* automatically inversion of TICs added* tic files will now be correctly inverted* bug in PCD import fixed* cursor up/down support added to preferences* import of compressed KOALA added* EXIF details will now be displayed in the information window* new command simplified* support for QuickTime movie display in the browser added* crash in IPTC save fixed* support for Power Windows improved* bug in display of folder icons in the browser fixed* problems with some radio button groups in the save prefs fixed* problems with some radio button groups in the prefs fixed* bug of paste in the browser fixed* zoom value change accept now the enter key, too* notification before save of large WBMPs added* edit of IPTC information of all selected files in the browser added* bug in saving a 16 bit image as PNG fixed* refresh problem in the browser fixed* loop in browser with 1 pixel row images fixed* option for displaying the JPEG compression dialog before save added* save of compression rate to JPEGs added* bug in displaying the icons in the broser fixed* bug in window refresh fixed* bug in index conversion in convert more fixed* bug in BMP RLE4 import and export fixed* bug in save of MacPaint fixed* bug in import of TGAs fixed* error detection in CGM import improved* error handling in EPOC import improved* Softimage import improved* bug in export of RLE4 compressed BMPs fixed* bug in icon creation (introduced with 3.7.3b0) fixed* bug in arrange windows fixed* error handling in TIFF import improved* redraw bug in the browser fixed* browser will display the finder icons if there is no preview* redirecting of a double click in the browser to the Finder added* bug in display of number of files fixed (if number is >32676)* bug in export of EPSF files fixed* split option improved* export of 16 bit bmps added* option to copy grayscale to RGB channel added* bug in uncompressed TIFF-CMYK import fixed* support for remembering last selecton dimensions added* arrow option to line added* bug with last entry in slideshow list fixed* bug with active swap frames menu item fixed* links to about dialog added* double click on an open image in the browser activates the image* two frame biorad files will now imported as an 32 bit image with a red and green content* bug with PCD files in the browser fixed (preview quality improved, too)Changes in 3.7.2:* import and export of PGC added* import of PGF added* import and export of wbmp (wireless bmp) (type 0) added* import of TIFF with 48 bits added* import of YC TIFFs added* import of CAM files from the new Casio digital camera added* import of CGM will now use VDC type 1 if there is no VDC type tag but a real tag* import of cicn improved* slice export improved (png support added, empty parts will no longer be saved)* EPSF import improved* many translation bugs fixed* option added for enlarging animated GIFs with frames outside the basis image* error handling in DICOM import improved* MIME decoding improved* option-click on sliders in brightness/contrast set the sliders to zero* rename/overwrite bug in slideshow fixed* move folder in slideshow will inform the user if the name already exists* bug in preview display of files with the same name fixed* skip automatic preview generation for files over maximum size added to browser prefs* support for Internet Config added (GraphicConverter can update the File Mapping Database)* editable zoom factor in the bottom left of the window added* remember previous values of brightness/contrast added* option to manually select vdc type for CGM added* lowercase option in catalog creation is now an option* option to edit creator of slices added* drawing bug of slice frames fixed* bug in saving slices with empty url strings fixed* bug in printing with scale factor fixed* option to save the preview with the full image added* bug in opening of grayscale Photoshop files fixed* bug in 16 bit raw import fixed* error handling of PCD import improved* undo will now remember the last display scale* rotate and mirror will now work with the slice rectangles* bug with white bar in slideshow fixed* support for import of TIFFs with lzw and fillOrder=2 added* multipage support for encoded files added* better preview creation for DICOMS in the browser* bug in import of non-planar multistripe uncompressed CMYK TIFFs fixed* bug in saving of EPSF files with PICT preview fixed* wrong resolution after scale with last values fixed